txt.en: 'Who dares to wake me? What is this disturbance?'
'Where is my help?'
Barashal
'Let our battle be at its end!'
'I have done my duty! You will never make it to the top in time!'
'My life serves to slow you. My death will not be forgotten!'
'My defeat means nothing! You will never defeat my lord!'
Angmarim Slaver
'Smash the bridges to pieces! Stop them at all costs!'
'You have lasted longer than I expected.'
'Now it is time for you to fall, [placeholder]!'
'You have proven to be a more difficult foe than I expected, yet I am not yet defeated.'
'You no pass!'
'You've saved me! Hurrah!'
'Well, well. I have been waiting for you to arrive.'
'Thank you! I will hurry back now!'
'Your name will be remembered always! Thank you!'
'Ahh, I see we have brave explorers.'
'It seems you have made a wrong turn, fools. Allow me to correct it!'
Lorniel
'What a marvelous place Mordirith has given us.'
'You dare to think you can enter this keep?'
'It begins... tarry too long, and you will meet your death at the top!'
'I applaud your courage, foolish though it may be.'
'Enough! I will end this!'
'Behold the power of Mordor!'
'We are being attacked! Save yourselves!'
Ornate Gate
'Arise, my bloodsworn!'
'Well done, [placeholder]!'
'Healers, lend me your power!'
Hi!
'You have had good fortune... but that shall soon change!'
'Carn DÃ»m is overrun. It is time to end this now.'
'I would not thought it possible that you could challenge me for so long....'
'Very well, you win! Come here....'
'Angmar will one day rule all of Eriador!'
'I am proud to wear the robes of the Angmarim!'
'Amarthiel has been missing as of late.'
'Can you believe no one wanted this place?'
'I have heard that Mordirith speaks with the Great Eye himself.'
'Now let us see if you can withstand the combined power of Mordor and Angmar!'
'Intruders! Where did they come from?'
Barashal roars, 'Smash the bridges to pieces! Stop them at all costs!'
'Why thank you so kindly. I was trapped in there!'
'Impressive... now the real challenge begins....'
'Do you think me weak because Golodir's accursed blade is still lodged in my chest?'
'You have come far, but no further.'
'I must leave you to deal with these fools. Mordirith has asked to speak with me.'
'Lazy fools! Help me!'
'Stop dancing and come kill them!'
Iron Grate
'You go no further!'
'Perhaps I am... then again, perhaps I am not.'
'Enjoy the fall, fools!'
'Let us put it to the test and see who is the stronger!'
'This is the end for you!'
'You are to be commended. You have withstood all that I have set against you.'
Ornate Grate
